# Styling

This project uses SCSS for styling with the following structure:

- [styles/index.scss](mdc:styles/index.scss) - Main style entry point
- Bootstrap 5 is used as a CSS framework
- The application has support for theme switching (light/dark mode)

Animation libraries:
- AOS (Animate On Scroll) for scroll animations
- react-animated-cursor for custom cursor effects
- Slick Carousel for slider components